<font color="#FF0000">CD-ROM: BEYOND THE WALL</font><br>
<tt>Sun Nov 24 17:53:41 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
Wanted to mention a nice CD-ROM you can get for Windows and Macintosh called &quot;Beyond the Wall: Stories Behind the Vietnam Wall&quot; by Magnet Interactive and Fox Home Entertainment. It recently won the New Media Magazine Imedia Awards Best of Show 1996. I have seen it for sale at Borders books and the Windows version for rental at my video store.<br>
I was an assistant designer (to lead designer Alice Kreit) on it. (I no longer work there so this is not a plug...) <br>
It is nicely done and very moving. Check it out.
